      A smoothie is a beverage made by pur√©eing ingredients in a blender. A
      smoothie commonly has a liquid base, such as fruit juice or milk, yogurt,
      ice cream or cottage cheese. Other ingredients may be added, including
      fruits, vegetables, non-dairy milk, crushed ice, whey powder or
      nutritional supplements. A daily smoothie can offer a super convenient way
      to get your fruits and veggies in while also nourishing your body with
      many essential vitamins and minerals. The key is to maximize those
      benefits by focusing on whole, nutrient-dense foods while avoiding added
      sugars as much as possible.
